{
  "info": {
    "name": "A2Z Auth API",
    "description": "Authentication module for the A2Z Modular Monolith.\n\nPhone-based OTP authentication with JWT token management.\n\n## Flow\n1. **Send OTP** → Request a 6-digit OTP to your phone number\n2. **Verify OTP** → Submit the OTP to authenticate and receive JWT tokens\n3. **Refresh Token** → Use the refresh token to get a new access token\n\n## Environment Variables\n- `base_url` — Server base URL (default: `http://localhost:8000`)\n- `access_token` — Auto-populated after successful OTP verification\n- `refresh_token` — Auto-populated after successful OTP verification\n- `phone` — Phone number for testing",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "phone",
      "value": "9876543210",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Authentication endpoints — OTP-based login and token refresh.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Send OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{phone}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/send-otp",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "send-otp"]
            },
            "description": "Sends a 6-digit OTP to the provided phone number.\n\n**Rate Limit:** Max 5 requests per phone number within a 15-minute window.\n\n**OTP TTL:** 5 minutes (300 seconds).\n\n> ℹ️ In development, the OTP is logged to the server console as:\n> `[SIMULATED SMS] -> Sending OTP <code> to <phone>`"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/send-otp",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "send-otp"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"OTP sent successfully\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Missing Phone",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/send-otp",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "send-otp"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Phone is required\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Rate Limited",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/send-otp",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "send-otp"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Too Many Requests",
              "code": 429,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Too many OTP attempts. Please try again later.\"\n}"
            }
          ],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response has success flag', function () {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.message).to.eql('OTP sent successfully');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "console.log('✅ OTP sent! Check server console for the OTP code.');"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify OTP",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{phone}}\",\n  \"otp\": \"000000\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/verify-otp",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "verify-otp"]
            },
            "description": "Verifies the 6-digit OTP against the stored value in Redis.\n\nOn success:\n- Returns JWT access & refresh tokens\n- Returns user info (id, phone, role)\n- Indicates if this is a new user (`isNewUser`)\n- Auto-creates a `customer` user if phone is new\n\n> ⚠️ Replace the `otp` field with the actual OTP from the server console."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success — New User",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"otp\": \"482917\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/verify-otp",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "verify-otp"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": {\n      \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890\",\n      \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n      \"role\": \"customer\"\n    },\n    \"tokens\": {\n      \"accessToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\",\n      \"refreshToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\"\n    },\n    \"isNewUser\": true\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Success — Existing User",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"otp\": \"482917\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/verify-otp",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "verify-otp"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"user\": {\n      \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890\",\n      \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n      \"role\": \"customer\"\n    },\n    \"tokens\": {\n      \"accessToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\",\n      \"refreshToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\"\n    },\n    \"isNewUser\": false\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Invalid OTP",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"otp\": \"000000\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/verify-otp",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "verify-otp"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Invalid or expired OTP.\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Missing Fields",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9876543210\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/verify-otp",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "verify-otp"]
                }
              },
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Phone and OTP are required\"\n}"
            }
          ],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response contains tokens', function () {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.tokens.accessToken).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.tokens.refreshToken).to.be.a('string');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Auto-save tokens to collection variables",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', json.data.tokens.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', json.data.tokens.refreshToken);",
                  "    console.log('🔑 Tokens saved to collection variables.');",
                  "    console.log('👤 isNewUser:', json.data.isNewUser);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Issues a new short-lived access token using a valid refresh token.\n\nThe refresh token itself is NOT rotated — it remains valid until its own expiry.\n\n> 💡 The `refresh_token` variable is auto-populated after a successful Verify OTP request."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/refresh",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "refresh"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
